Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:38.04,Title,,0,0,0,,KIMI K3 IS NOT A NORMAL MODEL
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:38.04,Tag,,0,0,0,,@ashen_one  •  FULL VIDEO CLIPPED BY PROMETHEUS
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.38,Caption,,0,0,0,,The Chinese have done it again, but this time they're coming for our fable five tokens
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.22,0:00:05.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,and credits.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.06,0:00:11.42,Caption,,0,0,0,,No, I'm joking, so K3, Kimi K3 came out this week, and it is supposed to be the world's
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.24,0:00:16.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,strongest open weight model ever, even beating fable five on certain benchmarks.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.64,Caption,,0,0,0,,But as you know on this channel, we don't really listen to these benchmarks because
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,we can't even read to begin with.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.30,0:00:24.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,We only care about certain tests, like how good is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.32,Caption,,0,0,0,,Like how fast is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.82,Caption,,0,0,0,,How cost effective is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.82,0:00:30.96,Caption,,0,0,0,,How does it compare to other leading models, like 5.6 Sol, or even Opus 4.8?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.14,Caption,,0,0,0,,Because fable five, even...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.14,0:00:37.80,Caption,,0,0,0,,And of course, how well can it recreate Minecraft, which we'll go over later in this
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,video.